      passage: `<p>The fossil remains of the individual known as LD 350-1, discovered in Ethiopia in 2013, can help paleoanthropologists not only ______ steps in the evolution of hominids but also illuminate the Pliocene epoch generally, revealing important details about the time in which LD 350-1 lived.</p>`,
